{"tid":1219513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】立法會外深宵平靜 警戒備森嚴　3小時前","createTime":"2019-06-13T22:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T22:26:32.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"32b6cf554413f58e2faa5277f7920293145e5aaf","tid":1219513,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T22:09:40.000Z","msg":"前日（12日）立法會外「反送中」示威者與警方爆發衝突後，警方至今仍封鎖前往立法會及政總的道路，昨晚深夜曾有市民與警員對峙，至凌晨大部份人已散去。<br />\n<br />\n在通往中信大廈的行人天橋，被警方用鐵馬攔住，有三名教徒坐在地上唱聖詩，數名警員在場監視。附近一帶仍戒備森嚴，包括速龍小隊警員周圍巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GN8ufSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGN8ufSQ.jpg&h=a55b3065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gvUxdEw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgvUxdEw.jpg&h=ac1ad609&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88ff5058dbdbb96cca56c95690f8743b09edf1ab","tid":1219513,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T22:09:51.000Z","msg":"【引渡惡法】立法會外深宵平靜 警戒備森嚴　<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190614&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59713456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190614%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59713456&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=3bef8fd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190614%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59713456&h=273e7d44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190614&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59713456</a>"},{"pid":"975ec19902e51afca3812ec04fcb290253657483","tid":1219513,"uid":135517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T22:10:23.000Z","msg":"我宣佈《保民生 反修例 大聯盟》正式成立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1218758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1218758</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"25fbdc00867724c38d3e1d4995ed1c20870a99c3","tid":1219513,"uid